text: Autoerotic can refer to: * Autoeroticism - the practice of becoming sexually stimulated through internal stimuli * Erotic target location errors (ETLEs) - a class of sexual interests in which sexual arousal depends on imagining one's self in another form, such as an animal, child, or the other sex. * Autoerotic (film), a 2011 film by Joe Swanberg.
title: Autoerotic
